# project name - Image Slider


#description
This project is a simple and responsive Image Slide created using HTML,CSS,JAVASCRIPT.
The Slider allows the user to navigate the images using"previous" and "next" buttons,and it alsoplaysautomatically every 3 seconds.

# features
Auto image slider slideshow
Previous/next buttons
Responsive layout for mobile and desktop
- Responsive layout for mobile and desktop
- Smooth transitions
- Clean UI design

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## How to Run the Project
1. Download or clone the project folder.
2. Open `index.html` in any web browser.
3. Add your images inside the `images` folder.


## File Structure
- index.html – Main HTML file
- style.css – All styles
- script.js – Slider logic
- /images – Folder containing slider images

